CatDescriptText: Mrs. Eva Gaines, 7-1/2 Bloomer Way, was part of the Pittsburghers Speak Up column published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 8, 1958, pg. 2 with question: "Should jitney drivers be licensed and permitted to operate, or should they be jailed?" answer reads: "They should have a license to operate, because this would make the taxicabs servet he people better."
